---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact — Arsovo"
  description="Get in touch with the Arsovo team."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 mb-6">Contact</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-800">
      <p>
        The fastest way to reach us is email.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>General inquiries:</strong>
        <a href="mailto:hello@arsovo.com">hello@arsovo.com</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Corrections or factual issues with a post:</strong>
        <a href="mailto:editorial@arsovo.com">editorial@arsovo.com</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Business &amp; partnerships:</strong>
        <a href="mailto:business@arsovo.com">business@arsovo.com</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Response time</h2>
      <p>
        We aim to reply within 2&ndash;3 business days. If you don't hear back within a week, please send a
        follow-up — spam filters sometimes eat things.
      </p>

      <h2>Suggest a topic</h2>
      <p>
        If you want us to benchmark a specific AI coding tool, compare two setups, or cover a workflow,
        tell us which one and what you're curious about. Practical, reproducible tests are exactly what
        this publication is for.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
